source: TEXT_LUCKMD102_03607_SEQ_00<tab>Alisaie is contemplating all that must yet be done in the wake of battle.
TEXT_LUCKMD102_03607_YSHTOLA_000_010<tab>Take a deep breath for me. That's it...
TEXT_LUCKMD102_03607_ALISAIE_000_020<tab>The others are helping to treat the wounded. I'm planning to assist in moving them, but even so, we simply don't have enough hands.
TEXT_LUCKMD102_03607_ALISAIE_000_021<tab>I'm sure you're fit to fall over after what we've been through─gods know I am─but if you could see to a few of the patients, it would be an enormous help.
TEXT_LUCKMD102_03607_ALISAIE_000_022<tab>Captain Lyna is about somewhere, so you might also consider asking her if there are any other outstanding areas of need. We'll talk later.
TEXT_LUCKMD102_03607_ALISAIE_000_025<tab>Just hold on. You'll be in the next carriage back to the Crystarium, I promise...
TEXT_LUCKMD102_03607_SYSTEM_000_031<tab>With tear-filled eyes, the prone man gazes up at you. His fingers twitch, as if to reach for you, but he lacks the strength to raise his hand.
TEXT_LUCKMD102_03607_INJUREDB03607_000_035<tab>If I turn, please... Please, kill me, I beg you.
TEXT_LUCKMD102_03607_INJUREDC03607_000_038<tab>I killed her... I killed her! She was one of them, I know, but I... <sob>
